{"tid":2151017,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"襲警被捕後遭圍毆 全身傷兼眼角膜受損 官裁定受警威嚇招認口供全不可呈堂 16:00裁決","createTime":"2020-08-11T07:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T10:05:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":105,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b565c1096efa3e2fdbdcb75ac1847641553142b4","tid":2151017,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/6OZKYPZUTQMBOCBXI7ZLMELUOE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2F6OZKYPZUTQMBOCBXI7ZLMELUOE%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FrhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=6778a971\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2F6OZKYPZUTQMBOCBXI7ZLMELUOE%2F&h=a68bd991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/6OZKYPZUTQMBOCBXI7ZLMELUOE/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年10.1有市民將立法會議員何君堯的相片貼在港鐵太子站外，便衣警見狀將文宣「踢甩」，引發警民衝突。中年漢被指踢了警員一腳，遭多名防暴警圍毆，繼而被控襲警罪，案件今在西九龍裁判法院續審。裁判官林子勤指，被告事後傷勢嚴重、眼角膜受損，但警方卻將他扣押30小時、完成三份會面紀錄後才將被告送院。林官認為，被告當時不適合在未經診治下錄取口供，並指招認是在警員威逼和誘導下作出，裁定警方錄取的三份警誡會面紀錄全不可呈堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8032&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FrhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=45e376d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8032</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第十三庭 <br />\n<br />\n休庭至1600裁決"},{"pid":"2b39495657e0ea7a6e1c5ce0d7c387087a295807","tid":2151017,"uid":189157,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">用酷刑逼供又冇後果?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a5431a213b51cad276046e3984a6d1974256fbf8","tid":2151017,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/